title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Berliner Park is the biggest park of its size in Central Ohio.” [From the 6 p.m. newscast on 21 October 1984, Channel 6 TV, Columbus, Ohio. Submitted by Dorothy Branson, Columbus, Ohio.]
